### Inventory API — run after auth from auth.http (sets {{token}})

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@characterId = 1
@campaignId = 1
@classId = 1

### Get starting equipment options for Fighter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}/starting-equipment-options
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get character inventory
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/characters/{{characterId}}/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Submit starting equipment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/characters/{{characterId}}/starting-equipment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weaponItemId": 4,
  "armorItemId": 9,
  "shieldItemId": 20
}

### Equip item (set inventoryItemId from inventory response)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/characters/{{characterId}}/inventory/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "equipToSlot": "main_hand"
}

### Unequip item
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/characters/{{characterId}}/inventory/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "unequip": true
}

### Update gold
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/characters/{{characterId}}/gold
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gold": 25
}

### Get attacks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/characters/{{characterId}}/attacks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List campaign items (reference + homebrew)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create campaign item (master only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemType": "gear",
  "name": "Potion of Healing",
  "description": "Restores 2d4+2 hit points.",
  "value": 50,
  "weight": 1
}

### Grant item to PC (master only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/playable-characters/{{characterId}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": 41,
  "quantity": 1
}
